{"tid":619010,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人咁鍾意質疑醫護","createTime":"2018-04-06T09:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T10:30:28.000Z","uid":138740,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71db5d1ac52f95b7190c8136cb2c9d176b3a3cfc","tid":619010,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"我指個啲當自己咩都識嘅人<br />\n真係屌 如果識咁多 係咁質疑人 <br />\n又做咩去睇呢<br />\n<br />\n你話你講嘅野合理都算<br />\n有啲一聽落就知唔合理嘅<br />\n人地解釋你又唔聽<br />\n仲喺到鬧鳩人<br />\n哇屌咁勁 自己醫自己啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做你嘅屋企人喺你隔離聽住你講都覺得樣衰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0dc2c24c954201f5a0619ce9893c801815836d","tid":619010,"uid":171177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98c35d379666febada86ee5895d615c44588ae98","tid":619010,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b36af249084dfd3d36fc0a41cb108ba84a5bd82","tid":619010,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"香港人全世界最長命,點解呢唔通食好住好?"},{"pid":"e5c3577799aec79565e3cd881d54674a15b8fc19","tid":619010,"uid":150294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b36af249084dfd3d36fc0a41cb108ba84a5bd82","tid":619010,"uid":173227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"香港人全世界最長命,點解呢唔通食好住好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"長命唔代表有質素！<br />\n香港始終地方細，唔會你暈左喺街幾個鐘都冇人理失救致死。但救返又如何？ 分分鐘半身不遂，失禁又講唔到嘢咁過多十幾二十年先埋單，有閪屎用咩！"},{"pid":"c7b01b3171732f37c917df792b296fdcd2925dfb","tid":619010,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0dc2c24c